    <briefdescription>
<para>This class is an alternative to directly invoking <ref refid="classMR_1a643e3be78f578a2f6adacd0d29612444" kindref="member">meshToDirectionVolume</ref> for the mesh retrieved from the teeth mask. It is better because when a single mesh is created from mask, some neighboring teeth might fuse together, creating incorrect mask. This class invokes meshing for each teeth separately, thus eliminating this problem. Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1TeethMaskToDirectionVolumeConvertor" kindref="compound">MR.TeethMaskToDirectionVolumeConvertor</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
